{"lemma":"فَصْلُ","slug":"فَصْلُ","root":"ف.ص.ل","root_slug":"ف-ص-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ص-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فَصْل","root":"فصل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":9},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":19},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33998","n34001"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فَصَلَ (faṣala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"separation, division, partition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"decision"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"incision"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"season"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chapter, paragraph, division"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"class (group of students)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"joint"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"interstice, gap"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"point"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"difference"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sagacity"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"conclusive, decisive (speech)","tags":["invariable"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to separate, to divide","tags":["invariable"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to judge between (+بَيْنَ (bayna))","tags":["invariable"],"examples":[{"text":"إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ يَفْصِلُ بَيْنَهُمْ يَوْمَ الْقِيَامَةِ فِيمَا كَانُوا فِيهِ يَخْتَلِفُونَ"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fire (from a job)","tags":["invariable"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wean","tags":["invariable"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go away, to leave","tags":["invariable"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to detail","tags":["invariable","transitive"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33998","headword_ar":"فَصَلَ","root":"fSl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolN","text_ar":"فَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He separated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put apart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) a thing, (S, O, Msb, *)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano gayorihi","text_ar":"عَنْ غَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from another thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoDahu mino baEoDK","text_ar":"بَعْضَهُ مِنْ بَعْضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano baEoDK","text_ar":"عَنْ بَعْضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part thereof from part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"myz","text_ar":"ميز"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made a separation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"partition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahumaA","text_ar":"بَيْنَهُمَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA *) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between them two,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning, two things,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making it known that the former had come to an end:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says Er-Rághib: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala AlHad~u bayona AlA^aroDayoni","text_ar":"فَصَلَ الحَدُّ بَيْنَ الاَرْضَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor. and] inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The limit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"boundary, made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"formed, a separation between the two lands:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSalotu bayona Alqawomi","text_ar":"فَصَلْتُ بَيْنَ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made a division,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separation, between,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among, the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala Alr~DiyEa Eano A^um~ihi","text_ar":"فَصَلَ الرّضِيعَ عَنْ اُمِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almawoluwda","text_ar":"المَوْلُودَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani Alr~aDaAEi","text_ar":"عَنِ الرَّضَاعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) aor. as above,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2406},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiSaAlN","text_ar":"فِصَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolN","text_ar":"فَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the former is a simple subst., (M, K,) or both, (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He weaned"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the suckling from his mother,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the young infant from sucking the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, M, Mgh, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AftSlhu","text_ar":"افتصلهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSalati AlmaroA^apu raDiyEahaA","text_ar":"فَصَلَتِ المَرْاَةُ رَضِيعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolN","text_ar":"فَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiSaAlN","text_ar":"فِصَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the subst.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the woman weaned her suckling."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  Hence also, i. e. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala","text_ar":"فَصَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as first expl. above,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolu AlxuSuwmaAti","text_ar":"فَصْلُ الخُصُومَاتِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The deciding of litigations, altercations,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disputes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolu AlxiTaAbi","text_ar":"فَصْلُ الخِطَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or this latter means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinct,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plain speech; which he to whom it is addressed distinctly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plainly, understands; which is not confused,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dubious, to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh in explanation of it in the Kur xxxviii. 19, and Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as decides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinguishes, between what is true and what is false,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh ibid., Mgh, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and what is sound and what is corrupt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh, Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and what is correct and what is erroneous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as decides the judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judicial sentence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the evidence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proof, that is obligatory"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as a condition of his justification]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the claimant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plaintiff,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the oath that is obligatory"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in like manner]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon him against whom the claim,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plaint, is urged;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh, O, K; [an explanation of which a part is dropped in the CK;]) thus accord. to 'Alee: (Ksh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"using of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^am~aA baEodu","text_ar":"اَمَّا بَعْدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ksh, O, K. [Respecting this phrase, and for other explanations, see 3 in art"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTb","text_ar":"خطب"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalimapu AlfaSoli","text_ar":"كَلِمَةُ الفَصْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Kur xlii. 20 means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sentence of God's deciding between mankind"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the day of resurrection, (O,) which is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu AlfaSoli","text_ar":"يَوْمُ الفَصْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaSolu","text_ar":"الفَصْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone] means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The deciding judicially between what is true and what is false;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, K;) and, (O, K,) sometimes, (O,) so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfayoSalu","text_ar":"الفَيْصَلُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) or this latter is [a simple subst, i. e.,] a name for such decision; (TA;) and is also an epithet [expl. below]. (M, O, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA yawomu A@ld~iyni h`*aA yawomu A@lofaSoli","text_ar":"هٰذَا يَوْمُ ا@لدِّينِ هٰذَا يَوْمُ ا@لْفَصْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur xxxvii. 20 and 21, means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is the day of requital:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"this is the day wherein a decision,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a distinction, shall be made"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yufoSalu fiyhi","text_ar":"يُفْصَلُ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the doer of good and the doer of evil, and every one shall be requited for his work and with that wherewith God will favour his servant the Muslim."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a rab~aka huwa yafoSilu bayonahumo yawoma A@loqiyaAmapi fiymaA kaAnuwA","text_ar":"اـِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ يَفْصِلُ بَيْنَهُمْ يَوْمَ ا@لْقِيَامَةِ فِيمَا كَانُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi yaxotalifuwna","text_ar":"فِيهِ يَخْتَلِفُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur xxxii. 25, means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily thy Lord"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He shall decide"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between them"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and distinguish what is true from what is false,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the day of resurrection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by distinguishing the speaker of what is true from the speaker of what is false, in respect of that wherein they used to disagree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of what concerned religion. (Bd.) And one says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala AlHukoma","text_ar":"فَصَلَ الحُكْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[He decided"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judicial sentence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala Aln~aZoma","text_ar":"فَصَلَ النَّظْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the K, is a mistake: see 2. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala mina Aln~aAHiyapi","text_ar":"فَصَلَ مِنَ النَّاحِيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino Albaladi","text_ar":"مِنْ البَلَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano baladika*aA","text_ar":"عَنْ بَلَدِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwlN","text_ar":"فُصُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the part of the country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the town"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from such a town"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala","text_ar":"فَصَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEasokaru Eani Albaladi","text_ar":"العَسْكَرُ عَنِ البَلَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The army went forth from the town"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: whence the saying of the Prophet respecting Ibn-Rawáhah,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna A^aw~alanaA fuSuwlFA","text_ar":"كَانَ اَوَّلَنَا فُصُولًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA=xirunaAqufuwlFA","text_ar":"وَا=خِرُنَاقُفُولًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was the first of us in going away"},{"kind":"text","text":"(↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinofiSaAlFA","text_ar":"اِنْفِصَالًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":") from his house and his family"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the last of us in returning"},{"kind":"text","text":"to [it and] them. (Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala fulaAnN mino EinodiY","text_ar":"فَصَلَ فُلَانٌ مِنْ عِنْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwlN","text_ar":"فُصُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one went forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from my presence"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vicinage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala min~iY","text_ar":"فَصَلَ مِنِّى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbu A_ilayohi","text_ar":"كِتَابُ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A letter"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passed from me to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Thus the verb is intrans, as well as trans.; its inf. n. when it is trans, being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolN","text_ar":"فَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; when intrans.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwlN","text_ar":"فُصُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala Alkaromu","text_ar":"فَصَلَ الكَرْمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The vine put forth small grapes, resembling lentils"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a grain similar thereto."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","O","Msb","K","TA","Mgh","Ksh"]},{"entry_id":"n34001","headword_ar":"فَصْلٌ","root":"fSl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of the trans. v."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSala","text_ar":"فَصَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. passim]. (M, Msb, K, TA.) [As a simple subst., it has various significations here following: and is] sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwlN","text_ar":"فُصُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A separation, division,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"partition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"between two things. (M, K.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoSil","text_ar":"مَفْصِل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"joint,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"articulation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and therefore"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the division, of two bones"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of the body: between every one such and another [that is the next to it] is a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wiSol","text_ar":"وِصْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or limb, in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waSol","text_ar":"وَصْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, O, K.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoSilN","text_ar":"مَفْصِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-  As used by the Basrees, [in grammar,] it is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A disconnective"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EimaAdN","text_ar":"عِمَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as used by the Koofees: (O, K:) thus in the saying in the Kur [viii. 32],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_no kaAna h`*aA huwa A@loHaq~a mino Einodika","text_ar":"اـنْ كَانَ هٰذَا هُوَ ا@لْحَقَّ مِنْ عِنْدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If this, it, be the truth from Thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hw","text_ar":"هو"},{"kind":"text","text":"is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fSl","text_ar":"فصل"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EmAd","text_ar":"عماد"},{"kind":"text","text":", [more commonly the former,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHq~","text_ar":"الحقّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the accus. case as being the predicate of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kAn","text_ar":"كان"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) ―         -b5-  Also sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwl","text_ar":"فُصُول"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwlu Als~anapi","text_ar":"فُصُولُ السَّنَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The four divisions of the year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"autumn, winter, spring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"summer"},{"kind":"text","text":"], expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zmn","text_ar":"زمن"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zamanN","text_ar":"زَمَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A division,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"section, of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAb","text_ar":"باب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chapter"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as being divided from others, or as forming a division between itself and others, so that it has the meaning of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or that of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MF, TA.) ―         -b7-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSolN","text_ar":"اَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as denoting relationship]: there are"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSuwl","text_ar":"اُصُول"},{"kind":"text","text":"of relationship and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuSuwl","text_ar":"فُصُول"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof; [the former meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stocks"},{"kind":"text","text":"and] the latter meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branches."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb. [See also other explanations of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolN","text_ar":"فَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^SolN","text_ar":"اصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"under the latter of these words ;)       -A2-  [It is also used as an epithet;] One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolN qawolN","text_ar":"فَصْلٌ قَوْلٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A true say or saying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not false:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus in the Kur [lxxxvi. 15]: (M.) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSolN","text_ar":"فَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The final character is unclear in the original text."},{"kind":"text","text":"there means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinguishing between what is true and what is false:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and relates to the Kur án [itself]. (Ksh, Bd, Jel.) And it is said of the speech of the Prophet that it was"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSalN laAnazorN walaA","text_ar":"فَصَلٌ لَانَزْرٌ وَلَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ha*arN","text_ar":"هَذَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA, but in the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ha*orN","text_ar":"هَذْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[to assimilate it in form to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nazorN","text_ar":"نَزْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"],) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Distinct,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plain, distinguishing between what is true and what is false;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not little are much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A general"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAEuwn","text_ar":"طَاعُون"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plague"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pestilence"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA"]}]}}